section.section:
The offer to each tenant shall be made concurrently with the giving of the notice required by § 5-6B-05 of this subtitle, shall be a part of that notice, and shall state that:
The offer will terminate upon the earlier to occur of termination of the lease by the tenant or 60 days after delivery;
Acceptance of the offer by a tenant who meets the criteria for an extended lease under § 5-6B-07(b) of this subtitle is contingent upon the tenant not receiving an extended lease;
Settlement cannot be required earlier than 120 days after acceptance by the tenant; and
The household is entitled to reimbursement for moving expenses as provided in subsection (h) of this section.
